                            <p>For Premium Members that are looking to increase their online presence, we offer several extended services to boost exposure both on and away from Lawyer.com. TopFirm Listings, or custom ads that appear above all featured lawyer profiles, are our most valuable product to date and provide the greatest visibility within our directory.</p>
                            <br>
                            <p>TopFirm Listings can showcase an individual lawyer or firm on a county, state, or nationwide scale. Countywide ads, which are our most popular version, retail for the low price of only $199 per practice area and can be displayed within any county in the United States. For instance, a lawyer who has an office in Ventura County, CA, but pulls clients from all of Southern California, may instead choose to position their ad within Los Angeles County to market to a larger population.</p>
                            <br>
                            <p>Our design team customizes the HTML for each TopFirm Listing to make the ad as effective as possible. All TopFirms feature an expanding custom image that will catch the eye of potential clients, a prominent phone number to generate calls, and multiple links to drive visitors to the lawyer's website, blog, and social media. </p>
